  "description": {
    "zh": "你的传记肯定很有趣，“塔科夫射手”，多棒的绰号啊？接下来会是什么？“精神病狙击手”？哦，得了吧，别逗了，但说真的，你应该自己读读，你知道的。很多 shady actors，有些人对你的了解比你自己还多，如果你仔细想想，这很可怕，所以我建议你做你的事，并尽快尝试离开塔科夫……除非你属于这里？\n\n聊够了，好吧好吧。你有工作要做，不过有时候讲个小故事很重要，你不觉得吗？当然，你不会载入史册，至少我是这么认为的，但你绝对会成为当地的传奇！看看你之前的经历，我不认为这对你来说会是一项困难的任务，对吧？当然不是，看看你！你是专业人士。你肯定能搞定，毫无疑问。",
    "en": "Your biography surely is interesting, \"Tarkov Shooter\", what a nickname huh? What's gonna be next? \"Psycho Sniper\"? Oh come one, give me a break, but in all honesty, you should read it yourself, you know how it is. Lots of shady actors, some people know more about you than yourself, it's pretty scary if you think about it, so I suggest you do your thing and try to get out of Tarkov as soon as possible... Unless you belong here?\n\nEnough talk, alright alright. You have work to do, sometimes a little story time is important though, don't you think? Sure, you won't be in the history books, at least that's what I think, but you will definitely be a local legend! Looking at your previous history, I don't think I would be wrong to think that this won't be a difficult task for you, right? Of course not, look at you! You're a pro. You'll manage, without a doubt."
  },
